|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q108487214}} (Uda District) - {{ill|Iku Kuni no Miyatsuko|ja|伊久国造|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Iku Kuni no Miyatsuko|qq=|1=Iku Kuni no Miyatsuko|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q85876227}} (Igu District) - {{ill|Shi Kuni no Miyatsuko|ja|思国造|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shi Kuni no Miyatsuko|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} (Shida District) *** * Listed south to north. No Kuni no Miyatsuko is associated with the namesake districts of Aizu (Iwasu Province) or Namekata (Ishikami Province).
